StoredProcedureSqlServerv2k5.name: [sp_GetDependentHistory]
StoredProcedureSqlServerv2k5.body:
@PersonID int AS
SELECT CD.DEPENDENT_ID, D.DEPENDENT_TYPE_DESCRIPTION, CD.LAST_NAME, CD.FIRST_NAME, CD.MIDDLE_NAME, CD.SUFFIX_CD, CD.VERIFICATION, CONVERT(CHAR(11), CD.DATE_OF_BIRTH, 106) AS DATE_OF_BIRTH, CD.DEPENDENT_TYPE FROM CANDIDATE_DEPENDENT CD INNER JOIN DEPENDENT D ON (CD.MARINE_CANDIDATE_ID = @PersonID AND CD.DEPENDENT_TYPE = D.DEPENDENT_TYPE)
